0C1F7A21.Line13.B20BA: No. It’s time I finish what the fires could not.

3FD4C12E.Line5.10B961: What gave you pause, I wonder?

5D201C8E.Line1.B20BA: You should have stayed in Brione, Stana. Burned with the rest.

6751176C.Line3.10B961: And you should have aimed higher. A gut wound like that was quite the gamble - and very unlike you.

F0DC14B2.Line9.10B961: Come, Torben. Help me rekindle the Days of Ash. Bring back those fires that gave us so much life.
